								| 
								span.text_color_green Выкуплен
								br
								| Оплачено 5680&nbsp;₽
								
						.card-basket__column.card-basket__column_control: .card-basket__control.cp: .cp-basket__container
							.cp-basket__column: button.cp-basket__button: svg.svg(width="13" height="13"): use(xlink:href="images/sprite.svg#remove")
							.cp-basket__column: button.cp-basket__button: svg.svg(width="16" height="16"): use(xlink:href="images/sprite.svg#edit")
							.cp-basket__column: button.cp-basket__button: svg.svg(width="16" height="16"): use(xlink:href="images/sprite.svg#share")
				
			.section-basket__buttons
				a.section-basket__button.button.button_theme_green.button_size_xs(href="#") Сохранить заказ
				a.section-basket__button.button.button_theme_yellow.button_size_xs(href="#") Оформить заказ
